natural alpha male qualities completely,

32:16.436 --> 32:20.399
and I doubt you can,
be a Gary to Larry Hall.

32:20.899 --> 32:22.651
Make him feel like you're his brother.

32:22.734 --> 32:25.654
Always looking out for him, never judging.

32:28.824 --> 32:29.825
All right.

32:32.077 --> 32:33.078
Well…

32:34.997 --> 32:36.498
We've got a plane to catch.

32:37.082 --> 32:38.083
What?

32:39.960 --> 32:41.920
