33:13.785 --> 33:15.120
Doing well.

33:16.955 --> 33:18.123
How you doing?

33:20.501 --> 33:21.793
Here.

33:22.878 --> 33:25.088
You gotta put them back on
when we get to Springfield,

33:25.172 --> 33:26.757
