34:02.459 --> 34:03.502
You scared?

34:10.801 --> 34:12.010
I'll get over it.

34:13.762 --> 34:14.804
Don't.

34:15.889 --> 34:20.101
Comfortable people get cocky,
and cocky people fuck up.

34:21.478 --> 34:22.771
