Right?

36:06.250 --> 36:07.835
Don't let the clock rule you.

36:07.918 --> 36:10.712
Don't approach Hall too early,
or he'll know we sent you for him.

36:11.547 --> 36:14.049
-I hear you.
-Besides the warden and Dr. Zicherman,

36:14.132 --> 36:15.592
