39:58.649 --> 39:59.983
Is that how you see it?

40:02.277 --> 40:04.613
Who put that idea into your head, Larry?

40:04.696 --> 40:08.951
Now, why does everybody think I need
my ideas to come from someone else, huh?

40:10.202 --> 40:13.163
I'm smart. I've got ideas.

40:14.039 --> 40:15.415
I'll bet you do.

40:16.041 --> 40:18.043
I'd like to hear about a couple of 'em.

40:18.627 --> 40:20.546
Maybe ones that involve girls?

40:23.382 --> 40:24.925
Gary got me a lawyer.

40:26.218 --> 40:27.719
So it was Gary.

40:28.220 --> 40:29.847
Yeah, but-- No, but…

40:30.597 --> 40:33.559
