another word to you.

40:33.642 --> 40:34.643
Is that right?

40:35.602 --> 40:38.647
Well, I don't know if that lawyer
is looking out for you, in my opinion.

40:38.730 --> 40:41.233
'Cause you twist what I have to say.

40:41.316 --> 40:43.443
