and you signed a confession.

40:49.491 --> 40:50.659
Which was coerced!

40:50.742 --> 40:51.785
No.

40:51.869 --> 40:53.203
The confession was coe--

40:55.914 --> 41:00.002
We are coming, Father Abraham
300,000 more

41:00.085 --> 41:01.461
Hey, Larry. Take it easy.

41:01.545 --> 41:02.838
From Mississippi's winding stream…

41:02.921 --> 41:04.006
Larry.

41:04.798 --> 41:08.927
We leave our plows and workshops
Our wives and children dear

41:09.011 --> 41:12.222
With hearts so full of utterance
With but a silent tear

41:12.306 --> 41:13.974
Hey. Take it easy, all right?

41:14.057 --> 41:17.769
We are coming, Father Abraham
300,000 more

41:17.853 --> 41:21.481
From Mississippi's winding stream
And from New England's shore

41:21.565 --> 41:22.733
Okay.

41:33.285 --> 41:34.453
You got kids?

41:35.704 --> 41:38.415
Yeah, I got a son. He's five.

41:39.541 --> 41:43.670
Man, loved five. It's the perfect age.

41:43.754 --> 41:45.214
