for the second appeal on the docket.

46:20.822 --> 46:22.950
Oh, fuck off. Really?

46:23.033 --> 46:24.993
Keene's not moot anymore.

46:25.494 --> 46:28.372
-We need him to step way up.
-I told him to move slowly.

46:28.914 --> 46:30.374
