47:19.840 --> 47:20.966
Sorry about that.

47:24.011 --> 47:25.304
Welcome to Springfield.

47:38.734 --> 47:39.902
Empty your pockets.

47:50.162 --> 47:51.997
All right, clothes go in there, bud.

47:52.539 --> 47:53.582
