48:20.025 --> 48:21.193
Here you go.

48:21.735 --> 48:22.778
Follow me.

49:03.485 --> 49:04.653
Chow's in ten.

49:05.153 --> 49:06.488
Which way?

49:06.572 --> 49:09.283
Just follow the crazy train, bud.

49:09.366 --> 49:10.450
Hang in there.

49:10.534 --> 49:11.785
First week's the toughest.

49:45.444 --> 49:46.445
How's it coming?

49:49.239 --> 49:51.116
It's pretty fucked up.

49:52.034 --> 49:53.410
