49:55.954 --> 50:00.918
A machine is like a--
It's like a person, Mr. Burden.

50:02.127 --> 50:03.754
Hygiene matters.

50:04.588 --> 50:07.049
And this boiler,
it was neglected for years.

50:07.132 --> 50:10.469
That neglect has allowed
for filth to spread everywhere.

50:10.552 --> 50:16.350
Every crevice is infected,
every valve, every locknut.

50:18.519 --> 50:19.686
So, how long?

50:28.362 --> 50:30.155
Want me to bring you something
from the mess?

50:30.906 --> 50:33.242
Yeah, just a sandwich.

50:33.325 --> 50:34.409
Will do.

50:34.493 --> 50:35.494
Thank you.

51:29.548 --> 51:31.884
